message.entry: The phase noise level must be negative.
The lengths of the phase noise level and frequency offset vectors must be the same.
The sample rate must be greater than twice the maximum value of the frequency offset.
The frequency offset vector must be monotonically increasing.
Current combination of phase noise level and frequency offset may produce inaccurate results.
The frequency resolution of the spec is greater than can be achieved. Consider increasing the minimum frequency offset and/or difference between specified frequency offsets.
